      <head>Ludwig Scheibler</head>

      <div>
        <p>Art historian and music historian. Among his publications was <title level="m">Geschichte
            der Kölner Malerschule</title> (1894-1902).</p>


        <p>Scheibler published a monograph on <title level="m">Franz Schuberts einstimmige Lieder,
            Gesänge, und Balladen mit Texten von Schiller</title> in 1905. Together with
          <ref cRef="entity-000164">Otto Erich Deutsch</ref>, Scheibler was one of the key figures in early Schubert scholarship.</p>
        
        
        <p>There is no known correspondence between Scheibler and Schenker. His name arises in
        correspondence with Otto Erich Deutsch.</p>
      </div>
